Android Bluetooth Low Energy Discover

Copyright (c) 2013 Mathias Claes


BLE (Bluetooth Low Energy) Discover let you easely discover Bluetooth Smart devices.
Bluetooth low energy (BLE) branded as Bluetooth Smart is a wireless computer network
technology which is aimed at novel applications in the healthcare, fitness, security, and home entertainment industries.
BLE Discover let you operate in two modes, Central and Peripheral.
It allows you to scan and connect to devices and has the ability to set up your own Bluetooth GATT profiles.


